  "prompt": "Should I text my crush first?",
  "response": "Whether you should text your crush first depends on your comfort level and the context of your relationship. Here are a few things to consider:\n\n1. **Interest Level**: If you feel a good connection and think they might be interested too, sending a text can show your initiative.\n\n2. **Previous Interactions**: Reflect on your previous conversations. If you've had engaging interactions before, reaching out may feel natural.\n\n3. **Timing**: If you\u2019ve just met or recently had a meaningful conversation, it might be a good time to follow up.\n\n4. **Your Personality**: If you\u2019re generally more outgoing and confident, texting first can align with your personality. If you\u2019re more reserved, it\u2019s okay to take your time.\n\n5. **Relaxed Approach**: You could start with something light or casual\u2014this can make it easier and less pressure-filled.\n\nUltimately, if you want to text them, go for it! Good luck!",
